            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "margin": "0",
              "color": "#0dcd7b"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content2",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"content2 mbr-section article\" plugins=\"amp-main\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters> \n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-row mbr-justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-col-sm-12 mbr-col-md-10 mbr-col-lg-8\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-section-title mbr-light\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Certified in Google Adwords</b></h3>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article><b>Start Your Google Adwords PPC Campaigns&nbsp;!</b> <br>Google has recognized me as a Google Ads certified professional, meaning that I’ve passed multiple assessments that assess my product expertise. I’m qualified to help you grow your business on the web using Google Ads:\n<br>-Search Advertising\n<br>-Mobile Advertising\n<br>-Video Advertising\n<br>-Display Advertising\n<br>-Shopping Advertising \n<br>Start Your Google Adwords PPC Campaigns\n<br>The goal of this work is to make your Adwords campaign a success by building on top of your SEO strategy to improve rankings and conversions. \n<br>This work will kick start your Adwords campaigns and set up your account following Google and industry practices to increase your conversions. \n<br>What you get with this work: \n<br>- Search campaign creation. \n<br>- Ad groups and ads creation. \n<br>- Positive and negative keywords research and set up. \n<br>- Demographic set up (age, gender, language, location, device and platform). \n<br>- Technical set up (budget, bid, ad scheduling). \n<br>- Adwords campaign performance dashboard. &nbsp;<br><br><b></b></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "rH2Q1g25lF",
          "_anchor": "content2-8",
