          "_name": "content18",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"mbr-section content18\" group=\"Article\" plugins=\"amp-main\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\">\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"../_images/background3.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-container\">\n        <h2 mbr-if=\"showTitle\" class=\"mbr-title align-center mbr-fonts-style mbr-bold mbr-white\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\">Google Adwords Certified .\n</h2>\n        <h3 mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" class=\"mbr-section-subtitle align-center mbr-light  mbr-fonts-style mbr-white\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>What is an Adwords / Google Ads Consultant?</b></h3>\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-btn align-center\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd,-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-success\" href=\"index.html#contacts2-9\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Get In Touch</a></div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "rH4hW94taH",
          "_anchor": "content18-e",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".mbr-text": {
              "margin-bottom": "0",
              "color": "#15181b"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "margin": "0",
              "color": "#0dcd7b"
            }
          },
          "_name": "content2",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"content2 mbr-section article\" plugins=\"amp-main\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters> \n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-row mbr-justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-col-sm-12 mbr-col-md-10 mbr-col-lg-8\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-section-title mbr-light\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Google Adwords Certified</b></h3>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article><b>What is an Adwords / Google Ads Consultant?</b><br><b><br></b>What is an Adwords / Google Ads Consultant? A Google AdWords consultant is a paid search expert on the Google search engine. His goal will be to generate qualified traffic on his client's website. It usually works for e-merchants or lead generators who have a complete web marketing strategy and want to set up or optimize Google Adwords campaigns. Its goal will be to achieve the best return on investment (ROI) for its customers.\n<br>\n<br>He does not work directly for Google but has an official Google Partner certification as well as many years of experience in managing paid search campaigns.\n<br>\n<br>We can also name it: Expert in sponsored links, Traffic Manager, Freelance Adwords, Google Adwords Agency&nbsp;<br><br><b>What are his missions?</b><br><br>By working with a Freelance Adwords consultant he will be brought to:\n<br>\n<br>- Analyze your sector, the potential of your business to generate profitable Adwords campaigns based on your current conversion rate.\n<br>\n<br>-Set up your account and goals correctly by also checking that Google Analytics works well to get the set of statistics\n<br>\n<br>-Determine an organization of campaigns, ad groups, and campaign types to set up\n<br>\n<br>-Choose and propose the right keywords with the right targeting (exact keywords, regular expressions, broad queries ...)\n<br>\n<br>-Setting up your campaigns by determining ROI at attet constant optimization of your ROI\n<br>\n<br>-Write ads that make you want to click and add various extensions to boost the click rate of the ad.\n<br>\n<br>-Perform a rigorous management of manual or automatic bidding according to your objectives and volume.\n<br>\n<br>-Make regular reports to its customers to be in continuous optimization phase, especially by optimizing the quality level of keywords.\n<br>\n<br>-Reduce acquisition costs and increase the conversion rate of your site for an equivalent budget.\n<br>\n<br>-An Adwords Consultant (or PPC Expert) takes care of the audit of existing campaigns to the creation of new campaigns, up to tracking and analysis of results.&nbsp;<b><br></b><br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
