          "_name": "content2",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"content2 mbr-section article\" plugins=\"amp-main\">\n    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters> \n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-row mbr-justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-col-sm-12 mbr-col-md-10 mbr-col-lg-8\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style mbr-section-title mbr-light\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Install and configure Google Analytics and Google Tag Manager</b></h3>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article><br>About this work\n<br>Services that we provide:\n<br>1. Create and share access to Google Analytics or Google Tag Manager.\n<br>2. Set the Google Analytics or Google Tag Manager code to the site.\n<br>3. Full configuration of the resource and view in Google Analytics, or full customization of the Container and tags in it in Google Tag Manager.\n<br>4. Set up goals in Google Analytics and link events to them from Google Tag Manager.\n<br>5. It is also possible to make an individual quest for your tasks.&nbsp;<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
